# V1 Architecture Overview

The V1 codebase implements a terminal-based LLM chat application with potential Gmail integration.

## Core Components

- Main entry point: [v1/src/main.cpp](mdc:v1/src/main.cpp) - Implements the TUI and application flow
- LLM Interface: [v1/src/LlamaInference.cpp](mdc:v1/src/LlamaInference.cpp) and [v1/inc/LlamaInference.h](mdc:v1/inc/LlamaInference.h) - Handles model loading and inference
- Tool Management: [v1/src/tool_manager.cpp](mdc:v1/src/tool_manager.cpp) and [v1/inc/tool_manager.hpp](mdc:v1/inc/tool_manager.hpp) - Framework for tool calls
- Python Bindings: [v1/src/python_bindings.cpp](mdc:v1/src/python_bindings.cpp) and [v1/inc/python_bindings.hpp](mdc:v1/inc/python_bindings.hpp) - Gmail API integration

